\": 1108, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"an elbow injury\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"full strength\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell is undeterred.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nothing's a given.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"a given\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there is an opportunity for me to win that gold on the day, you know that my team will put it on the bar and I will give it my best crack.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"my team\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"my best crack\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, I will stand up with it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell carries the weight of British hopes on her shoulders in Paris as the nation's only entrant in the sport.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9987867029359309, \"rank\": 0.000964646946985183, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999977817424, \"rank\": 2.2183228576217207e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"her shoulders\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has achieved almost everything there is to achieve - European champion, Commonwealth champion, plus world and Olympic silver medals - but there is still work to do, still medals of a golden hue left to grasp.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999636384025, \"rank\": 3.622905110130171e-08, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1818694161491025e-13, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost everything\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"world and Olympic silver medals\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"still medals\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden hue\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always had a list of goals that I wanted to tick off,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a list\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"goals\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am nearly there, I have nearly done them, but the list is not complete.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as long as the list is not complete, I am always going to have that fire.\\\"\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"that fire\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her rise has been fuelled by a positive outlook on life and on sport.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her rise\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive outlook\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell has been the victim of online abuse and body shaming along the way, and has risen above it to become an inspirational figure who exudes body positivity, proud to be one of the most powerful women on the planet.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the victim\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"body\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspirational figure\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"body positivity\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the most powerful women\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had two amazing parents that have always raised me to believe in how unique I am and to capitalise on that,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two amazing parents\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father moved to Britain from Jamaica as a young boy and grew up with little.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2448, \"end\": 2455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998780577688948, \"rank\": 0.00011909222680773358, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2461, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998076419, \"rank\": 1.9168374758238202e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her father\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"a young boy\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years ago, he watched as both Emily and her younger sister Kelsie competed at the Commonwealth Games - Emily for Britain and Kelsie, a swimmer, representing Jamaica.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2626, \"end\": 2633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998780577688948, \"rank\": 0.00011909222680773358, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2670, \"end\": 2677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998076419, \"rank\": 1.9168374758238202e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both Emily\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"her younger sister\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"Kelsie\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"the Commonwealth Games - Emily\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"Kelsie\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimmer\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For my parents that was a very special moment.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"a very special moment\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My dad always said, 'No one's gonna give you anything in life, you have to work really hard for it'.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dad\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one big lesson they always taught us was that it's all right to fail.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one big lesson\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how we learn, by making mistakes.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mistakes\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something I have always carried with me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What we are doing is not normal.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as you would love to be injury free, it's not realistic Without this try-anything mentality, Campbell might never have discovered the sport.\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was a field athlete in her teens, throwing discus, shot put and hammer with promise, but some way short of Olympic medal potential.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a field athlete\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"her teens\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"discus\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"shot\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"promise\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medal potential\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her coach at Leeds Beckett University who encouraged her to try weightlifting as a training method, and she quickly discovered a new talent.\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leeds Beckett University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifting\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"a training method\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"a new talent\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her road to Paris has not been smooth.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999977817424, \"rank\": 2.2183228576217207e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her road\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She went without central funding for several years and worked as a teacher in a special needs school alongside training to pay the bills.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"central funding\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"several years\", \"from\": 3538, \"to\": 3551}, {\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"a special needs school\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3601}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"the bills\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her Olympic silver medal helped secure the backing to train full-time, but wrist and back injuries have hampered her progress since a golden 2022 of European and Commonwealth glory.\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3801, \"end\": 3813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.1818694161491025e-13, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her Olympic silver medal\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3663}, {\"ngram\": \"the backing\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3708}, {\"ngram\": \"wrist and back injuries\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3737}, {\"ngram\": \"her progress\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Injury is a desolate place in weightlifting, perhaps even more so than other sports.\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Injury\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"a desolate place\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifting\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3865}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no other way we can train,\\\" Campbell explains.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3945, \"end\": 3953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no other way\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not like if you are a runner and you can not quite run for a bit, then you can get on the bike and you can still keep a certain amount of fitness.\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a runner\", \"from\": 3990, \"to\": 3998}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4034}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4064}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain amount\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For us to get strong, you have to lift weights.\\\"\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4123}, {\"ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Few sports tread such a fine line between exertion and injury.\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Few sports\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"such a fine line\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"exertion\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4217}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every muscle in the body is activated, and building them requires stress on the body - especially the knee and wrist joints, and the spine - which can trigger a serious setback to an athlete's career and a threat to their livelihood.\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every muscle\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4254}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4302}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4314}, {\"ngram\": \"especially the knee\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"wrist joints\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4353}, {\"ngram\": \"the spine\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4368}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious setback\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4406}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's career\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"their livelihood\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What we are doing is not normal.\", \"from\": 4464, \"to\": 4497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as you would love to be injury-free, it's not realistic.\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is always light at the end of the tunnel.\\\"\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"the tunnel\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Funding has given Campbell access to technology to help curate training based on more than gut feel.\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4635, \"end\": 4643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Funding\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4624}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4664}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"gut feel\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She uses an ergonomic tracker strapped to the bar which measures speed, path and power to monitor how she is moving, and whether her form and technique is controlled enough on a given day to justify increasing weight.\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ergonomic tracker\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4747}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4767}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4788}, {\"ngram\": \"path\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4804}, {\"ngram\": \"her form\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 4855}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4869}, {\"ngram\": \"a given day\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4905}, {\"ngram\": \"increasing weight\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 4934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was hard adjusting to full-time training, which meant a change in mindset and expectation.\", \"from\": 4937, \"to\": 5030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full-time training\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"a change\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5002}, {\"ngram\": \"mindset\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 5018, \"to\": 5029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it opened her eyes to what she could achieve.\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's when I started to realise possibilities were endless,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"possibilities\", \"from\": 5115, \"to\": 5128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campbell already has her life after sport mapped out and plans to open a gym that teaches children the core techniques for lifting weights and all the health benefits they bring.\", \"from\": 5155, \"to\": 5333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5155, \"end\": 5163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5184}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5191, \"to\": 5196}, {\"ngram\": \"a gym\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5231}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"the core techniques\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"all the health benefits\", \"from\": 5298, \"to\": 5321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People do not know that kids can start weightlifting from around six, seven years old.\", \"from\": 5335, \"to\": 5422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 5336, \"to\": 5342}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have technique bars, we have bumper plates.\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"technique bars\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"bumper plates\", \"from\": 5455, \"to\": 5468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the weight that they lift, it's about the body awareness.\", \"from\": 5470, \"to\": 5542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5495}, {\"ngram\": \"the body awareness\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about being able to move the body properly.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about physical literacy.\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"physical literacy\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about kids knowing that movement, fitness and sport is important for everybody in life.\\\"\", \"from\": 5622, \"to\": 5715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5637}, {\"ngram\": \"that movement\", \"from\": 5646, \"to\": 5659}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5668}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5678}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5705}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All that can wait.\", \"from\": 5717, \"to\": 5735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First, Campbell will try to upgrade Olympic silver to gold, against one of the greats of her sport.\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5743, \"end\": 5751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999228598456, \"rank\": 7.714020897730488e-08, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic silver\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5786}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 5790, \"to\": 5794}, {\"ngram\": \"the greats\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 30, in a discipline where the next injury could be just around the corner, this might be her last chance, but she will keep fighting to complete her tick list.\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a discipline\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"the next injury\", \"from\": 5865, \"to\": 5880}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 5902, \"to\": 5912}, {\"ngram\": \"her last chance\", \"from\": 5928, \"to\": 5943}, {\"ngram\": \"her tick list\", \"from\": 5984, \"to\": 5997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love getting on the platform.\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 6019, \"to\": 6031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love lifting weights.\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weights\", \"from\": 6048, \"to\": 6055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love trying to entertain people, and I know that my fire for that's not gone yet.\", \"from\": 6057, \"to\": 6140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6084, \"to\": 6090}, {\"ngram\": \"my fire\", \"from\": 6108, \"to\": 6115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am gonna keep doing that until the fire dwindles.\\\"\", \"from\": 6141, \"to\": 6193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6246, \"end\": 6257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.315855575666633e-21, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"ht